{"tid":722225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國軍方研發變型車輪　兩秒變履帶行走惡劣地型","createTime":"2018-06-29T09:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T15:59:39.000Z","uid":53379,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e035f0342b4b49101149bb83d3e7f23657752e45","tid":722225,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國軍方研發變型車輪　兩秒變履帶行走惡劣地型</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n戰場地型變化多端，使用日常的圓形車輪雖然夠在路面高速行駛，但在沙地或泥濘等惡劣地型時，履帶才能夠保障車輛不會卡住。為了讓軍車取得兩款車輪的優勢，美國國防高等研究計劃署（DARPA）設計了一款全新車輪，讓車輛可在行駛其間隨時轉用車輪或履帶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/28sub51new1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F28sub51new1.jpg&h=15e35432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實這車輪是美國政府 Ground X-Vehicle Technology（GXV-T）研究計畫的一部分。該計畫是為了提高軍用車輛的機動力，從而提升軍車的生存能力。這個名為「Reconfigurable Wheel-Track」的車輪能在 2 秒內，將圓形車輪變成三角形的履帶，增加車輛的接地面積，從而通過惡劣地型。整個變換過程可在行進中完成，車輪毋須停車，避免成為攻擊目標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/DARPA_technews_Jun-25-2018-17-09-55.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2FDARPA_technews_Jun-25-2018-17-09-55.gif&h=f4456100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/technews_Jun-25-2018-17-05-13-694x372.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Ftechnews_Jun-25-2018-17-05-13-694x372.gif&h=5bf51cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，除了這個技術外， GXV-T 計畫亦發表了直接將摩打安裝在車輪內等技術。研究計畫的負責人 Maj. Amber Walker 表示，十分期待將這些技術引入到未來的軍用車輛之中。研究小組更預計未來的軍車將能夠穿越包括斜坡等的95% 野外地形。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HrQrJ57J9eE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHrQrJ57J9eE&d=p%2Bwgd4HpTMwBOoDtTiDPlDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=6f5b8e82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HrQrJ57J9eE</a><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"http://defense-update.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdefense-update.com&d=p%2Bwgd4HpTMwBOoDtTiDPlDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=9c154df3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">defense-update.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/06/28/usa-trasforming-ties/life-tech/auto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2Fusa-trasforming-ties%2Flife-tech%2Fauto%2F&d=p%2Bwgd4HpTMwBOoDtTiDPlDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=eab15829\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/06/28/usa-trasforming-ties/life-tech/auto/</a><br />\n<br />\n支那好快又抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad8b7039aad89c9c161cf5097188d58f0a4c274","tid":722225,"uid":70786,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:03:45.000Z","msg":"支那軍摺被世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼子摺被摺到豆腐咁先好出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c14a717279678566500920898ab8e7e4d0d7b5d","tid":722225,"uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e0e373be06bb6698ebcb71896eaf1be15965bf","tid":722225,"uid":52358,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"中国好快又有自主研發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自煮燃發先啱"},{"pid":"d459725811210b123771f561c3e343e7cd5a8a24","tid":722225,"uid":83097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:01:26.000Z","msg":"支那 : 又出貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f874525e5b325643f84b7c81169e23e0f31e23","tid":722225,"uid":21028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cit